;; [1]: https://www.khronos.org/registry/OpenCL/sdk/2.0/docs/man/xhtml/atomic_cmpxchg.html
;; [2]: https://www.khronos.org/registry/spir-v/specs/unified1/SPIRV.html#OpAtomicCompareExchange
